show.title: THE FATE IS YOU
show.sharing_text: हेलो! मैंने कुकू एफएम पर इस शो को सुना और मेरे ख्‍याल से आपको भी पसंद आएगा
show.sharing_text_v2:
हेलो! मैंने Kuku FM (Android)  पर यह शो सुना और मुझे यकीन है कि आपको भी यह जरूर पसंद आएगा। 
https://links.kukufm.com/DGkcAh
show.description: Rescued by a stranger when his life is in danger, he sets out to find and thank the mysterious helper. Meanwhile, on the other hand, there is intense tension in a family—where a youngster is threatened with punishment to obey the orders of the elders. Mystery, emotion, and family chaos blend together in this story. The entire story weaves suspense and emotion in equal measure as it weaves between gratitude, searching for someone significant, and family conflict.
